<testgrp id="RM0000027E2000X_05_0008" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AON00000">
<testtitle>CONFIRM PART NUMBER OF SIDE AIRBAG SENSOR</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Check that the part number of the side airbag sensor LH is equal to the number of the other side.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Those numbers are the same.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect the connectors to the center airbag sensor assembly and the side airbag sensor LH.</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000027E2000X_05_0009" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM0000027E2000X_05_0010" fin="false">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000027E2000X_05_0009" proc-id="RM0250U___0000AOO00000">
<testtitle>CHECK SIDE AIRBAG SENSOR LH</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Interchange the side airbag sensor RH with LH and connect the connectors to them.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C123724E02" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Connect the negative (-) terminal cable to the battery, and wait for at least 2 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG), and wait for at least 60 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Clear the DTCs stored in the the memory (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000XFE00YX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG), and wait for at least 60 seconds.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Check the DTCs (See page <xref label="Seep02" href="RM000000XFE00YX"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Result</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC B1623, B1633, B1643, or 81 is output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC B1628, B1638, B1648, or 82 is output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>DTC B1623, B1633, B1643, or 81 and B1628, B1638, B1648, or 82 are not output.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
